-- (BUSINESS WIRE) -- Denodo requests that their press release NewsItemId: 20150921005618 entitled "Denodo Customer VHA to Discuss the Benefits of Data Virtualization at TDWI World Conference" be killed. 
The release was issued prematurely by Denodo. A replacement release will not be issued. View source version on businesswire.com: http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20150921005618/en/ Copyright Â© Business Wire 2015
